      "content": "i know, i know... \"help is available\" and all that. but it feels so hollow. it's not just a bad day, it's like my entire life was built around them and now there's just nothing left. how am i supposed to just \"move on\" when the person who made life worth living is gone? it feels more like i'm just waiting for the lights to go out anyway.",
